{"tid":263482,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"飲食狗想轉行","createTime":"2017-05-30T05:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T05:41:24.000Z","uid":33879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb56d5afa64f5c683764c85bf4d7135ae824431","tid":263482,"uid":33879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"做到有啲麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做飲食都做左兩年了<br />\n工作量太大 長期企同埋工時長<br />\n最重要係冇哂自己時間 有時朋友同家人想約下食飯都就唔到時間<br />\n所以最近想辭工轉行 唔想成世做死飲食<br />\n依家好迷惘 巴打有冇咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7485a8635e538eae954432d2f079abbf12d216af","tid":263482,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"考政府工"},{"pid":"a03bdb6c294cf282ec34a45476f471c1e7ee7bb3","tid":263482,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:13:06.000Z","msg":"飲食都唔係人做，工作經驗又無用，浪費人生"},{"pid":"bc503f3e1cf61380f54bfc99a9976abf5d226d77","tid":263482,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"做地盤囉"},{"pid":"af5e38d883bf4df8282b63d241c8067ca7db6c85","tid":263482,"uid":66590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:40:13.000Z","msg":"讀下書轉工 一係落地盤"},{"pid":"d1e1888219fcb0d50c466c04418a8a1438b87433","tid":263482,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"石廠"}]}